{
  "uid": "geosm-jaeger",
  "title": "GeOSM - Jaeger (metriques de tracing)",
  "tags": [
    "geosm",
    "jaeger",
    "tracing"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "A propos de ce dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Ce dashboard couvre les **metriques Prometheus exposees par Jaeger lui-meme**\n(ingestion/rejet de spans, latence de requetage, sante du processus Go) - scrutees via le job\nPrometheus `jaeger` (port admin 14269, voir `monitoring/prometheus/prometheus.yml`).\n\nPour **explorer des traces individuelles** (voir le detail d'une requete precise, son\ndecoupage en spans, les appels a Gemini/OSRM/Nominatim...), ce n'est pas un dashboard de\ngraphiques qui convient - utilise directement l'interface Jaeger :\n**[jaeger.geosm.app](https://jaeger.geosm.app)** -> onglet Search.\n\n> Note : les noms exacts de labels ci-dessous suivent les conventions standard de Jaeger\n> 1.52, mais n'ont pas pu etre verifies en direct. Si un panneau reste vide alors que\n> Jaeger recoit bien des traces, va dans Prometheus -> Graph et tape `jaeger_` pour voir\n> la liste exacte des metriques/labels reellement exposees, et ajuste la requete du panneau\n> en consequence (Grafana -> panneau -> Edit -> Query)."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Ingestion de traces (Collector)",
      "type": "row",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Spans recus/s par format",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(jaeger_collector_spans_received_total[5m])) by (format)",
          "legendFormat": "{{format}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Spans rejetes/s",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(jaeger_collector_spans_dropped_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Spans rejetes",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Longueur de la file de traitement",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "jaeger_collector_queue_length",
          "legendFormat": "File",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Latence de sauvegarde des spans (percentiles)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 15
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(jaeger_collector_save_latency_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(jaeger_collector_save_latency_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(jaeger_collector_save_latency_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "API de requetage (Query) - utilisee par l'interface Jaeger",
      "type": "row",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 23
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
